show.title: The Natural Nurse

title: November 1, 2010
content:
Ellen Kamhi PhD RN, The Natural Nurse, www.naturalnurse.com interviews Dr. Kem Moser, DDS. Dr. <!--more--> Moser is a Graduate of Temple School of Dentistry, Phila.
, Pa 1973, and is the current President of The Pennsylvania Cranio-Mandibular Society.
He is a Diplomat Board of American Academy of Dental Sleep Medicine and a Member of the International Association of Orthodontics.
Dr Moser specializes in “structural dentistry”.
Through this unique intervention he is able to help clients with orthodontic problems, headaches, migraines, neck and back pain and obstructive sleep apnea among other health issues.
